            <title>0.1.1</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jun 2026 00:57:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.1.1</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.1.1</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>Mingbai 0.1.1</h2>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Prevent hover lookups from triggering when the pointer is only near Chinese text.</li>
<li>Refresh permission-dependent hover state after local permission changes.</li>
<li>Restore hover lookups while still rejecting near-misses beside Chinese text.</li>
<li>Stop hover lookups from snapping to the first word of a line in apps (such as Messages) that report an unverifiable character position.</li>
<li>Fix hover lookup on large Chinese text embedded in images.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
